pageContext.claim: “These are Angry People, including the highly conflicted Bob Mueller, who worked for Obama for 8 years. They won't even look at all of the bad acts and crimes on the other side. ”
pageContext.analysis: Trump regularly suggests that Mueller is biased though he has not provided any evidence to support this claim. Plus, Mueller was initially appointed by George W. Bush. After his ten year term expired, Obama asked him to stay on. He stayed for two more years, meaning he served under Obama for four years, not eight.
